data.description: Exquisite Property in Premier Los Altos, Neighborhood, Long Beach.    Discover the epitome of luxury living in this stunning property boasting 3058 sq.ft. and offering 5 bedroom suites, 4 bathrooms, a versatile loft, and a spacious backyard perfect for family gatherings. With a two-car garage driveway, this cul-de-sac gem is situated in the prestigious Los Altos neighborhood, just 3 miles from Belmont Shore, 2nd Street, and the inviting beaches. California State University is a mere 1.7 miles, and recreational options abound with El Dorado Park Golf Course (2.8 miles), Planet Fitness (1.2 miles), and Colorado Lagoon (3.0 miles) nearby. Healthcare facilities such as Kaiser Permanente (1.7 miles) and Memorial Care Medical Group (3 miles) offer peace of mind. Immense yourself in culture at the Museum of Latin American Art and Long Beach Museum of Art. Convenience meets elegance, all just 9 miles from downtown Long Beach and 1.9 miles from Long Beach Airport. Don't miss this unique opportunity to own a slice of paradise in Los Altos
